Ingredients:

1 package (8 ounces) cream cheese, softened
1 jar (7 ounces) marshmallow creme
1 tablespoon lime juice
1 teaspoon grated lime peel
Dash ground ginger
Assorted fresh fruit

Directions:

In a large bowl, beat the cream cheese, marshmallow creme, lime juice, lime peel and ginger until smooth. Serve with fruit. Refrigerate leftovers. Yield: 2 cups.
